text: Urho Korhonen (14 June 1907 - 23 May 1971) was a Finnish gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1907 births Category:1971 deaths Category:Finnish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Finland Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vyborg
